OL,3,CStatue 'knocked off plinth' in storm
OL,4,Creturns to cemetery four years later
OL,6,FA marble statue has been returned to
OL,7,FArnos Vale Cemetery in Bristol after
OL,8,Fbeing badly damaged in a storm four
OL,9,Fyears ago.
OL,11,FIn the winter of 2021, the Hope
OL,12,FMonument took a hit from a tree branch
OL,13,Fand was knocked off its plinth.
OL,15,FIt was made in tribute to Anne
OL,16,FNielson, who died in 1860 at the age
OL,17,Fof 23. At the time, it gave hope to
OL,18,Fthose who knew her that she had gone
OL,19,Fon to a better place.
