OL,3,CStatue 'knocked off plinth' in storm
OL,4,Creturns to cemetery four years later
OL,6,FOne of the cemetery's long-standing
OL,7,Fvolunteers, Alan Bambury arranged to
OL,8,Fhave the sculpture restored by the
OL,9,Fstone masonry team at Bath College.
OL,11,FLecturers Paul Maggs and Steve Shute
OL,12,Fworked with students to clean and
OL,13,Frepair the delicate structure. Sadly
OL,14,FAlan died in summer 2023, before the
OL,15,Fwork was completed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
