OL,3,CStatue 'knocked off plinth' in storm
OL,4,Creturns to cemetery four years later
OL,6,FThe statue depicts hope as a woman -
OL,7,Fwith an anchor at her feet, a symbol
OL,8,Fof faith in Christ. She is in chains -
OL,9,Fbroken to show her life cut short but
OL,10,Fset free in the hope of eternal life.
OL,12,FThe stone masons were able to replace
OL,13,Fher fingers, mend part of her chain
OL,14,Fand also part of the anchor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
