OL,3,CStatue 'knocked off plinth' in storm
OL,4,Creturns to cemetery four years later
OL,6,FAnn Fiddler added: "She's made of
OL,7,Fmarble, which can make her slightly
OL,8,Ffragile as an outside statue. And we
OL,9,Fcan see that part of her chain has
OL,10,Fbeen repaired, and there is a
OL,11,Fpurposeful break in the chain as well,
OL,12,Fwhich does represent her life being
OL,13,Fcut short."
OL,15,FOn Friday 24 January 2025, Hope was
OL,16,Freturned to her original place on her
OL,17,Fplinth in the cemetery. It was a
OL,18,Ftricky operation involving scaffolding
OL,19,Fand slings and volunteers gathered to
OL,20,Fwatch and celebrate the completion of
OL,21,FAlan's project.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
